  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "These guys have done a fantastic job on our roof. They had patience and communicated clearly with us when giving our quote (very competitive by the way). They also were very timely and did a darn good job of getting this roof on. They were very respectful to my family and they cleaned up after themselves exceptionally well.  They pointed out little things along the way that they went ahead and fixed while up there which really saved us both time and money later on.\n\nI know we wont have to worry about a thing with our new roof, but if any of our friends have an issue, I know exactly who I'm recommending... A.M.T. Roofing for the win!!",
      "reviewer": "Hunter",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "If I could add more stars I would! Completely professional from start to finish.\n\nAsh’s expertise is outstanding. We’re delighted with our new roof. Super efficient, we felt completely at ease and took all his expert advice on board.\n\nWe had a new roof in our old house and the A.M.T crew were far superior. Competitive pricing and 100% professional. Amazing communication throughout.\n\nAsh is a total perfectionist, we even had our neighbours comment on how nice our new roof is!\n\nLocal business too! If you need a roofer and you can get them… book asap!",
      "reviewer": "Mr",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "AMT roofing carried out a complete strip off and re roof of my Victorian age property in Cardiff - 20/10 service and quality from the outset, even with the weather the guys worked solid and made sure everything was clean and tidy after every shift. Also replaced all my guttering / fascia / down pipes to a great standard. Would highly recommend to anyone. Thanks again AMT Roofing",
      "reviewer": "Michael",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Roof leak reported on Wednesday fixed by the Friday (would have been Thursday if not for the weather). Responded quickly after leaving a message and work was very professional and to high standard. Communication was clear with price set prior to work. Cannot recommend enough!",
      "reviewer": "Huw",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Ashley did a great job on our roof. Very professional and friendly at a good price - thanks again!",
      "reviewer": "Owen",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
